import React from "react"
import { Container,Stack,List,ListItem,Flex } from "@chakra-ui/react"

const App = ()=>{
  return (
    <Container maxW="800px">
      <Stack w="300px">
        <List p="4" minH="70vh" boxShadow="xl" borderRadius="md">
          <ListItem>Players</ListItem>
        </List>
      </Stack>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default App
